name: peacock feather print on organic cotton tan dress/skirt small one of a kind
description:
this organic cotton garment from global girlfriend can be worn as either a skirt or a dress. i tied the attached belt at the waist for a skirt and around my shoulders for the dress. it has 4% lycra giving the perfect amount of stretch. i printed ancient future's peacock feather in white across the front. it is a great staple piece with lots of flexibility for summer wear and layered for the colder seasons.

printed in white water based inks:
